name: Willow Creek
description:
Introduction

This beta (as well as HAZ) describes a nontechnical descent of Willow Creek, as the dry falls can be scrambled around on one side or the other.

Note: Pools at the base of each rappel seem to persist year-round so plan for B conditions (and anchor construction) if descending the watercourse with rope.
